OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F352A1775589082
OL,3,CFarmer reacts as new inheritance tax
OL,4,Crules come into force
OL,6,FChris Mallinson, a farmer from Wigton,
OL,7,Fgives his thoughts on the new tax
OL,8,Frules.
OL,10,FNew rules on inheriting farms in the
OL,11,FUK have come into force, after over a
OL,12,Fyear of debate and controversy.
OL,14,FFrom April 6 - the start of the
OL,15,Ffinancial year - a new levy on
OL,16,Finherited farms and family businesses
OL,17,Fworth over #2.5million will apply.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G1/8
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
