FL,353,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F352A1775589082
OL,3,CFarmer reacts as new inheritance tax
OL,4,Crules come into force
OL,6,FSpouses can pool their #2.5million
OL,7,Fallowances to make a total threshold
OL,8,Fof #5million, which represents a
OL,9,Fsignificant increase on the #1million
OL,10,Fthreshold originally proposed by the
OL,11,FGovernment in 2024.
OL,13,FChris Mallinson is a farmer in his
OL,14,Fearly 30s from Wigton. He grew up on
OL,15,Fhis father's farm, and hopes one day
OL,16,Fto pass the farm down to his children.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G2/8
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,353,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F352A1775589082
OL,3,CFarmer reacts as new inheritance tax
OL,4,Crules come into force
OL,6,FMr Mallinson told ITV Border: "Farmers
OL,7,Fare very disheartened, they feel
OL,8,Fthey've been attacked by the
OL,9,Fgovernment. It's been a million pound
OL,10,Fthreshold, and it's been upped to
OL,11,F#2.5m.
OL,13,F"It's a lot better for ourselves, but
OL,14,Fthere are loads of great farmers in
OL,15,Fthis area... big farms that have been
OL,16,Finherited over generations of farmers,
OL,17,Fand now all of a sudden they're being
OL,18,Fattacked by the government. It's easy
OL,19,Fmoney.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G3/8
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,353,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F352A1775589082
OL,3,CFarmer reacts as new inheritance tax
OL,4,Crules come into force
OL,6,F"I'm the fifth generation on the farm,
OL,7,Fand there's a sixth generation on the
OL,8,Ffarm - my boy George. But, to be
OL,9,Fhonest, I don't think there's a very
OL,10,Fgood future for farming."
OL,12,FThe specifics of the new inheritance
OL,13,Ftax rules have been strongly
OL,14,Fcriticised by farmers since they were
OL,15,Ffirst announced.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G4/8
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,353,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F352A1775589082
OL,3,CFarmer reacts as new inheritance tax
OL,4,Crules come into force
OL,6,FMr Mallinson said: "It was a massive
OL,7,Fstress on everybody, nobody was happy
OL,8,Fwith it. We've paid taxes on land that
OL,9,Fwe've purchased, everything we've
OL,10,Fbought, and farmers have (now) been
OL,11,Fattacked to get easy money.
OL,13,F"Everybody needs a farmer, 7-days-a-
OL,14,Fweek, 365-days-a-year. To my eyes,
OL,15,Ffamers are one of the backbones of
OL,16,FBritain."
OL,18,FThe Wigton farmer recognises that the
OL,19,Fincreased threshold will help his
OL,20,Ffarm, but says other farms will be hit
OL,21,Fby the new levy.
OL,26,@rD@ZpmrD@^pn
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G5/8
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,353,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F352A1775589082
OL,3,CFarmer reacts as new inheritance tax
OL,4,Crules come into force
OL,6,FHe said: "We're just a small family
OL,7,Ffarm, and with the threshold being
OL,8,Fraised, it's not going to effect us in
OL,9,Fthe way it was going to.
OL,11,F"It's gonna be a knock on effect for
OL,12,Fgenerations to come. If you're a big
OL,13,Ffarm with inheritance tax to pay...
OL,14,FIt's an old saying that farmers are
OL,15,Fasset-rich, cash-poor. They can't just
OL,16,Ffind a million pounds, or #100,000
OL,17,Fjust like that.
OL,19,F"It should just be abolished all
OL,20,Ftogether.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G6/8
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,353,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35207
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F352A1775589082
OL,3,CFarmer reacts as new inheritance tax
OL,4,Crules come into force
OL,6,F"They should up (the allowance) to
OL,7,F#5million, maybe #10million, to give
OL,8,Fthe working family farm a chance."
OL,10,FIn response to these comments, a
OL,11,FGovernment spokesperson said: "We've
OL,12,Flistened to farmers and raised the
OL,13,Frelief threshold to #2.5 million to
OL,14,Fprotect small family farms and
OL,15,Fbusinesses, while ensuring the largest
OL,16,Festates make a fair contribution so we
OL,17,Fcan deliver support for families and
OL,18,Fbusinesses, including cutting the cost
OL,19,Fof living."
OL,26,@nD@QpmnD@_pn
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G7/8
